name: Biffen's Kitchen
address: Ocean Pitch Campsite, Croyde, Braunton EX33 1FF England
about: Enjoy the taste of Croyde Surf-Inspired Street Food this summer at Biffen’s Kitchen. Come and find me (Biff) and my wonderful team at the Ocean Pitch Campsite. From Caribbean curry to Japanese Katsu, you cannot visit Croyde without devouring one of these dishes! EVERYONE IS WELCOME! You don’t need to camp at Ocean Pitch to enjoy my breakfast (8:30-10:30), Lunch (11:30-13:30) & evening street food (17:30-19:30). No-onsite parking is allowed as we are a small and busy campsite but parking is located close by. Your support is greatly appreciated and I look forward to seeing you soon, Biff

name: Kawaffle
address: Cornwall Street Stall 131 Plymouth Market, Plymouth PL1 1PS England
cuisine: British, Cafe, Fast food, International, Street Food
about: Take a seat and enjoy watching your sweet or savoury bubble waffle created right in front of you. Everything is made fresh on site daily. With delicious sweet toppings including locally made ice cream and branded chocolate bars and sweets! Our savoury toppings include Chilli Cheese, Chorizo, Avocado, Hummus, Mozzerella along with so many more. Offering amazing Vegan Gluten Free bubble waffles. All to takeaway or you're welcome to take a seat. Tea, Coffee, wonderful Milkshakes & Thick Hot Chocolate.

name: DillyDally Tearoom
about: We are a small award winning tearoom situated in the heart of Brixham's picturesque harbour area. We offer freshly made local sourced ingredients where possible which includes Gluten And Diary Free options. We offer freshly cooked breakfasts, a selection of light lunches, Devon Cream Teas (including Prosecco and Gin Teas) Afternoon Teas (booking required) and also a range of Homemade Cakes. We are dog friendly, and have an outdoor seating area weather permitting.
